{
  "stem": "1172.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we had to-- before we went to work, the cell floor had to be scrubbed with cold water.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't give us anything to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to scrub it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything had to be tip top.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They would come in and check and check and count us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know what they thought, [LAUGHS] that somebody could have disappeared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then we were led down to the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was a-- there were civilians with guns surrounding us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We found out later that these were Polish-- Polish people-- Polish men.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And one man in a leather coat with a red, long beard would make a speech.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Turned out he was a-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a man who was in charge of a German construction company.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He would give us a speech that if we work-- we go to work, then nobody can run away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If one disappears, ten will be shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they led us through Tallinn to a shipyard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That shipyard had been destroyed by the Russians when they moved back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we had, first, to clean up the rubble.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that took a while.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "After the rubble-- and it was winter then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was very cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After we had cleaned up the rubble, we had to-- a certain group of us young girls were taught brick laying.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Some women worked for deep sea-- for divers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Some were working in the factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were a group that was picked to learn bricklaying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So we had to start to build up the ship yard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So-- but we got extra food from the-- from the German company.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
